public void saveUser​(@PathVariable("username")
                     java.lang.String username,
                     @PathVariable("name")
                     java.lang.String name,
                     @PathVariable("password")
                     java.lang.String password,
                     @PathVariable("height")
                     int height,
                     @PathVariable("weight")
                     int weight,
                     @PathVariable("gender")
                     int gender,
                     @PathVariable("guestStatus")
                     int guestStatus)
        Save the user into the database
        Parameters:
        username - - the user's name as an email
        name - - the actual name of the user
        password - - the user's password
        height - - the height of the user
        weight - - the weight of the user
        gender - - the user's gender, 0 = male, 1 = female
        guestStatus - - whether the user is drunk or not
